snippet.title: Chimera CUSTOM XG - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam!
http://store.steampowered.com/app/2229900/Chimera_CUSTOM_XG

Join our Discord!
https://discord.gg/gkBmPm4zGu

You are a super soldier, a C.U.S.T.O.M. made by the Chimera project in a last ditch effort to save humanity. Dive deep into mysterious alien facilities, ancient structures, and hidden sites all over the planet.

Overcome technologically advanced defenses, deadly forces, and cunning traps. Be wary of what you uncover, as the most dangerous thing you may find is the truth!
